@Jonathan 
It looks like she was on Columbia from 1960-1966, Atlantic from 1966-1979, and Arista from 1980-2007.  As far as I can tell, she never recorded on the Motown label.
But I think Jonathan is right that "Motown" is referring to Detroit, where she lived for most of her life.  That's very tricky IMO for a Tuesday clue.  That's more like a Saturday clue.

@NH 
